1. Kada su mu ponudili posao u inostranstvu, novčana ponuda je bila njegov *mamac*. (When they offered him a job abroad, the financial offer was his lure.)
2. Ribolovci koriste *mamac* da bi privukli ribu. (Fishermen use bait to attract fish.)
3. Baka je iskoristila poslasticu kao *mamac* da bi unuče došlo da je poseti. (Grandma used a treat as a bait to make her grandchild come to visit her.)
4. Muškarci su se okupili oko stola gde se igrao poker i počeli da međusobno postavljaju *mamce* u vidu novca. (Men gathered around the table where poker was played and began to set lures to each other in the form of money.)
5. Ptice su padale u zamku koja je bila ispunjena *mamcem*. (Birds were falling into a trap that was filled with bait.)
6. Zaljubljena devojka koristi svoju lepotu kao *mamac* da bi privukla pažnju dečka. (A girl in love uses her beauty as a lure to attract the attention of a boy.)
7. Uprkos svom znanju i iskustvu, veterinar nije uspeo da prepozna *mamac* kojim su psi bili otrovani. (Despite his knowledge and experience, the veterinarian failed to recognize the bait that the dogs were poisoned with.)
8. Lovci su postavili *mamce* u vidu hrane da bi privukli divlje životinje. (Hunters set lures in the form of food to attract wild animals.)
9. Prodavci koriste *mamce* u vidu popusta da bi privukli kupce. (Sellers use lures in the form of discounts to attract customers.)
10. Glumci su koristili različite *mamce* kako bi publiku držali zainteresovanom tokom predstave. (Actors used different lures to keep the audience interested during the performance.)